dcterms:description: A dataset of synthetic instances for the Quadratic Assignment Problem (QAP) generated from a specific distribution, where locations are sampled uniformly at random in the two-dimensional unit square and the flow from facility i to facility j is sampled uniformly at random from [0, 1]. The flow matrix is made symmetric by adding it to its transpose and setting the diagonal elements to zero.
dcterms:title: Synthetic QAP Instances
